msgid "Sound editor"
msgstr "Editor (redactor) de sono"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kwave.appdata.xml:13
msgid ""
"Kwave is a sound editor that can record to, play, open, and edit many file "
"formats. Kwave makes it simple to edit audio in many ways."
msgstr ""
"Kwave es un editorde sono que pote registrar a, sonar, aperir e editar multe "
"formatos de file. Kwave lo face  semplice a editar audio in multe modos. "

